    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>火星需要你！</strong></i> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能怎么帮助它呢？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第一步：挖掘 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从你的矿机收集资源，探索它带给你的各种地形。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/574d712bd3e3f9e661a81e0243178ae4.poster.avif?t=1772327714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/574d712bd3e3f9e661a81e0243178ae4.webm?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/574d712bd3e3f9e661a81e0243178ae4.mp4?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >步骤二：构建 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用你找到的材料和武器，创造强大的毁灭机器，以击败攻击你家的机器人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用不同的武器来对抗你遇到的不同敌人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/aa83671710c8d13852d14032e5b52609.poster.avif?t=1772327714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/aa83671710c8d13852d14032e5b52609.webm?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/aa83671710c8d13852d14032e5b52609.mp4?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >步骤三：辩护 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抓起武器，向敌人的波涛发起猛烈攻击，使用子弹、火箭、炸药以及一切可以使用的武器。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/450bd491173673ac505ac78fe2369bcb.poster.avif?t=1772327714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/450bd491173673ac505ac78fe2369bcb.webm?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/450bd491173673ac505ac78fe2369bcb.mp4?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点 </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量物品 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从你的矿山开采矿物。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你挖掘的材料在商店购买物品。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你购买的物品建造炮塔。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护你的核心免受敌人的冲击。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武装自己，亲自用武器击倒敌人。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/89fe89dedb93966431e0a2d81a0746e8.poster.avif?t=1772327714\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/89fe89dedb93966431e0a2d81a0746e8.webm?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/89fe89dedb93966431e0a2d81a0746e8.mp4?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
